original_title: Mozart: Fantasia, K 397; Sonata, K 333, K 576
overview: Gulda's mastery of the classical repertoire is demonstrated as he plays a programme of compositions by Mozart, including, among others, the sonatas K 333 and K 576 and the FANTASIA K 397.
title: Mozart: Fantasia, K 397; Sonata, K 333, K 576
